WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
[Unknown]: आई वी एम

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:34.000
[Amit Varma]: Do u have a right to interfere and use force to stop the man with the stick?

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:37.000
[Amit Varma]: Any reasonable person would argue that you do

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:41.000
[Amit Varma]: You have both the right to defend yourself, as well as others who are at the receiving end of violence

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:44.000
[Amit Varma]: Such as that bleeding defenceless kid

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:46.000
[Amit Varma]: You might have doubts about practicality of it

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:49.000
[Amit Varma]: The gunda could have fellow gunda's around and you could get beaten up yourself

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:50.000
[Amit Varma]: So you may choose not to interfere

00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:53.000
[Amit Varma]: But there is no doubt about the morality of it

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:55.000
[Amit Varma]: It is right for you to intervene

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:57.000
[Amit Varma]: Now, here's a follow up question

